delivery:
Shipping

For orders placed before 9am IST, we endeavour to process the same business day. Orders placed after 12pm IST will be processed the next business day.

Free shipping in India!

All orders within India are free of charge. Please allow 3-5 business days for your goods to reach the destination after dispatch.

International orders are final sale and cannot be returned.

Returns

Before you return any of our products, please take a moment to understand what goes into making them. All our products are handcrafted with a lot of love and care, making each product special and unique. All the products go through a quality check before shipping.

  • Returns will not be accepted on damaged, used, washed or stained items.
  • Returns will not be accepted on Custom/Bespoke orders.
  • Return shipping methods and associated costs are the responsibility of the customer.
  • SALE products are final sales and are not eligible for return, refunds or exchange.

Please refer to our shipping & returns policy for more information.

  • Returns will not be accepted on damaged, used, washed or stained items.
  • Returns will not be accepted on Custom/Bespoke orders.
  • Return shipping methods and associated costs are the responsibility of the customer.
  • SALE products are final sales and are not eligible for return, refunds or exchange.

Please refer to our shipping & returns policy for more information.

Shipping

For orders placed before 9am IST, we endeavour to process the same business day. Orders placed after 12pm IST will be processed the next business day.

Free shipping in India!

All orders within India are free of charge. Please allow 3-5 business days for your goods to reach the destination after dispatch.

International orders are final sale and cannot be returned.

Returns
